One ex-girlfriend's little sister /did/ think my bus came from outer space.

I suppose they're just getting rarer and rarer. I did a u-turn in a 
elementary school lot once, and I swear both of the teams practicing peewee 
baseball stopped to stare at it. It's about the right color - must have 
looked like the funkiest school bus they'd ever seen.

